short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add official Google monthly search volumes to your Search Console keywords

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows you to import official Google search volumes (from the Google Ads Keyword Planner) into the performance report of your Search Console property. 

❯ Import search volumes for 7 languages and 13 countries
❯ Easily export the enriched data from your Google Search Console tables
❯ Download the full search volume report with data for the past 12 months to CSV

Please provide your feedback here: https://freesuggestionbox.com/pub/ybdvuif
